text: Hi <@U07DB91P073> you can get all the three details in the `Project Settings` of your Firebase project. Under the `General` tab you will find the Project ID, under the `Cloud Messaging` tab you would find the Sender Id and click on the Generate Key under the `Service Accounts` tab to generate the Service account JSON.
